# State Setup via API

Skip slow UI flows for setup!

## Real World Scenario

Testing a "Change Password" feature requires a logged-in user. If you log in via UI for every single test case, you waste massive amounts of time. Injecting auth tokens via API instantly puts the browser in the verified state you need.

